dc_title_s: Le duche de Bourgoigne et Comte de Charolois.; Dvche de Bovrgoigne et Comte de Charolois
dc_description_s: North oriented to the right. Includes illustrations of a face and vines of fruit around title and scalle cartouches. From "Atlantis Maioris Appendix", Johannes Janssonius, 1630. 1 map; 48 x 36 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Atlantis Maioris Appendix, 1630.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.,Hondius, Jodocus, 1594 or 1595-1629, cartographer.
